      "message": "FTR: this issue seems to be specifically an artifact of a \"nested\" try mapping to the same field. The following, for instance, does not result in the same error:\n\n```\n@experiment(try)\nnestedTry: emptyInnerInBody: {\n\t#foo?: foo2: int\n\tbar: {\n\t\ttry {\n\t\t\t#foo?.foo2\n\t\t\ty: { try {} }\n\t\t}\n\t}\n}.bar\n```\n\nThis seems to suggest to me that the implementation could be simplified.\nNeeds further investigation, but I figured I record this finding so far.",
